### This is my 2016 plan
In the first place, to work harder, earn more.

### to learn and practice a programming language.
To start my new project, i need to learn and practice a programming language. Learn more and think big.

### To package a system of own
learn more and practice more, to solve some problems in the process.

### Do not play that more games during the night.
Stop doing stupid things .

### this is what i want 
To have a new year and a uncertain future.
